令本身動搖緊既淺藍覺得恐懼"},{"pid":"3c77142845a6aaae11c6926b3d2d8f6e8b8efb32","tid":1351704,"uid":265111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T16:53:35.000Z","msg":"Pish<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b2e90ab8b66950401e5ea007cb44c15379927a1","tid":1351704,"uid":212182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T16:54:04.000Z","msg":"光復香港！"},{"pid":"75aa3eff53b51fb9823e29d2fb098719fa36ceb7","tid":1351704,"uid":12278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T16:57:31.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港！<br />\n時代革命！</span></span>"},{"pid":"88262577702309836cfff085f50cb02f467929fc","tid":1351704,"uid":37869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"788962f67e7e701af1a128a523b22c6a60ff9231","tid":1351704,"uid":12278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ed94032d54359cc4a69ffc0da9f779331f120540","tid":1351704,"uid":37869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T16:51:25.000Z","msg":"我老母話而家真係好似返左去六七十年代咁<br />\n警察就係黑社會 黑社會就係警察<br />\n諗住用恐懼嚇怕市民我諗可以叫佢慳d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n比起對未知的未來的恐懼<br />\n而家的恐懼只係小兒科<br />\n<br />\n喺條街都聽到d新移民討論<br />\n「有乜理由黑社會打人唔拉」"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T16:53:14.000Z","msg":"佢地呢個動作係想令本身動搖緊既淺藍覺得恐懼"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T16:59:04.000Z","msg":"淺藍係恐懼<br />\n但似乎恐懼令到唔少淺藍變黃"},{"pid":"ebf2d9a426e74a51fbbe8199ba3b5a808588af6d","tid":1351704,"uid":206284,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T17:00:10.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"e55133883ff02f2eb9217b18ece9090d3eedc046","tid":1351704,"uid":286877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T17:00:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ad30f24e0359ddcce0d63cfd136da74fcb7a8aed","tid":1351704,"uid":22675,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T17:00:49.000Z","msg":"From Simon Lui (Facebook)<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/photo.php?fbid=10156060495911105&amp;set=a.45435071104&amp;type=3&amp;sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fphoto.php%3Ffbid%3D10156060495911105%26set%3Da.45435071104%26type%3D3%26sfns%3Dmo&d=YNGzf4wH3lBRdiFquXkn2zIStCm0mHK7%2Bbmf%2BnNiY0c%3D&h=29255ebe\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/photo.php?fbid=10156060495911105&amp;set=a.45435071104&amp;type=3&amp;sfns=mo</a><br />\n<br />\n我經歷過波士頓馬拉松爆炸案，明白襲擊後的恐怖<br />\n1) 爆炸前30分鐘，我仍在Boylston st現場，只是早走了<br />\n2) MIT校警就在我Lab樓下(Building 32)被槍殺，只是我偷懶無返工(偷懶萬歲)<br />\n<br />\n我嗰晚好驚，本來諗住「一星期唔出街，以後見人都要提防」... 但原來我錯了<br />\n<br />\n【恐佈分子的目的，不是要讓100人死掉，而是要令幾億人害怕】<br />\n<br />\n是波士頓人教曉我，面對恐懼就要更勇敢。因為爆炸後第二晚，波士頓人竟然這樣：<br />\n- 不躲在家中，照常出街跑步<br />\n- 不讓恐懼擴散，反而故意外出食飯購物<br />\n- 人與人之間的信任沒有動搖。反而整網頁讓居民登記，開放自己家，讓因爆炸案錯過火車的旅人住一晚 <br />\n<br />\n「開放自己家！黐線㗎！引狼入室！」不是的<br />\n- 若恐佈分子要襲擊，點會無方法？<br />\n- 由華盛頓來旅行但錯過火車嘅自己人，點會睇唔出？幫佢點會有事？<br />\n- 自己人互相幫助，其實安全得很<br />\n- 所以最後，我自己都踩單車出去飲咖啡，重買水比站崗嘅人<br />\n<br />\n恐佈分子的失敗，在於居民鎮定不害怕，在於鄰里關係沒有動搖。若要防範恐佈分子，不是要人人自危，而是要把問題源頭清掉吧。<br />\n<br />\n香港人，守望相助，不要落單，齊上齊落<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"559cabbd8f2c634c075774d864aae736cc7f5413","tid":1351704,"uid":1430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T17:02:10.000Z","msg":"要活係恐懼之中同支那有咩分別！同做隻豬有咩分別！"},{"pid":"9dcc197711e5c6531d4bb28196226e7da7cda7ac","tid":1351704,"uid":266098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T17:03:48.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"018de8c439112d6603cb730feff5c11c8fd2c217","tid":1351704,"uid":12149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T17:04:26.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">請所有人針對返政權既黑暗, 元朗既事要處理, 但唔係最重要, 點解有元朗件事, 係因為呢個政權有份製造出黎!!!!!!!元朗班人遲早都要做condom, 針對政權, 處理黑警, 支線處理元朗!!</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"97c5d6c773132096cef9c5997c6a0dc977658f9f","tid":1351704,"uid":12278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ad30f24e0359ddcce0d63cfd136da74fcb7a8aed","tid":1351704,"uid":22675,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T17:00:49.000Z","msg":"From Simon Lui (Facebook)<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/photo.php?fbid=10156060495911105&amp;set=a.45435071104&amp;type=3&amp;sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fphoto.php%3Ffbid%3D10156060495911105%26set%3Da.45435071104%26type%3D3%26sfns%3Dmo&d=YNGzf4wH3lBRdiFquXkn2zIStCm0mHK7%2Bbmf%2BnNiY0c%3D&h=29255ebe\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/photo.php?fbid=10156060495911105&amp;set=a.45435071104&amp;type=3&amp;sfns=mo</a><br />\n<br />\n我經歷過波士頓馬拉松爆炸案，明白襲擊後的恐怖<br />\n1) 爆炸前30分鐘，我仍在Boylston st現場，只是早走了<br />\n2) MIT校警就在我Lab樓下(Building 32)被槍殺，只是我偷懶無返工(偷懶萬歲)<br />\n<br />\n我嗰晚好驚，本來諗住「一星期唔出街，以後見人都要提防」... 但原來我錯了<br />\n<br />\n【恐佈分子的目的，不是要讓100人死掉，而是要令幾億人害怕】<br />\n<br />\n是波士頓人教曉我，面對恐懼就要更勇敢。因為爆炸後第二晚，波士頓人竟然這樣：<br />\n- 不躲在家中，照常出街跑步<br />\n- 不讓恐懼擴散，反而故意外出食飯購物<br />\n- 人與人之間的信任沒有動搖。反而整網頁讓居民登記，開放自己家，讓因爆炸案錯過火車的旅人住一晚 <br />\n<br />\n「開放自己家！黐線㗎！引狼入室！」不是的<br />\n- 若恐佈分子要襲擊，點會無方法？<br />\n- 由華盛頓來旅行但錯過火車嘅自己人，點會睇唔出？幫佢點會有事？<br />\n- 自己人互相幫助，其實安全得很<br />\n- 所以最後，我自己都踩單車出去飲咖啡，重買水比站崗嘅人<br />\n<br />\n恐佈分子的失敗，在於居民鎮定不害怕，在於鄰里關係沒有動搖。若要防範恐佈分子，不是要人人自危，而是要把問題源頭清掉吧。<br />\n<br />\n香港人，守望相助，不要落單，齊上齊落<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T17:04:36.000Z","msg":"有催淚彈<br />\n香港人唔好驚呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不惟強權！"},{"pid":"35112d373fa0998b936e111a5a866e19e5b54510","tid":1351704,"uid":12278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T17:05:49.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">黑警可恥</span></span>"},{"pid":"7798e0328bf87192362fecd2e39d3ce43154379f","tid":1351704,"uid":232065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T17:06:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"283dede75338838256d65a14c448125560a8cc36","tid":1351704,"uid":80139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T17:08:54.000Z","msg":"光復香港<br />\n革命時代"},{"pid":"657448732a02adcdda9dd30ed0e398ee43f0d9e9","tid":1351704,"uid":12278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T17:09:02.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>光復香港！<br />\n時代革命！</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"81f6bf11e8700c258135bbd308fe2113f8e30812","tid":1351704,"uid":266503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T17:09:25.000Z","msg":"政權除了要我們恐懼多，還要製造仇恨。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1065677\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1065677&d=YNGzf4wH3lBRdiFquXkn2zIStCm0mHK7%2Bbmf%2BnNiY0c%3D&h=965226c4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1065677&h=892f01aa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1065677</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「人民不應該害怕他們的政府，政府應該害怕它的人民。」（People should not be afraid of their governments. Governments should be afraid of their people.）<br />\n<br />\n「藝術家用謊言揭露真相，政治家用謊言掩蓋真相。」（Artists use lies to tell the truth, while politicians use them to cover the truth up.）<br />\n<br />\n「沒有舞蹈的革命，是不值得發動的革命。」（A revolution without dancing is a revolution not worth having）<br />\n<br />\n「面具之下只是個血肉之軀，而在這面具之下的，還有一個理念，只不過，理念，是刀槍不入的。」（Beneath this mask there is more than flesh. Beneath this mask there is an idea, Mr.Creedy, and ideas are bulletproof..）<br />\n<br />\n「我們的尊嚴可能不值錢，但它卻是我們唯一真正擁有的東西。它是我們最後一寸領地，但在那一寸領地裡，我們是自由的。」（Our integrity sells for so little, but it is all we really have. It is the very last inch of us, but within that inch, we are free）<br />\n<br />\n「力量來自團結，團結來自信念」（Strength through unity, unity through faith）<br />\n<br />\n「恐懼往往是政府的終極武器。」（Fear became the ultimate tool of this government）<br />\n<br />\n「就算政府擁有的武力統治不讓人民發言，自由的言論仍然充滿著強大的力量。」（the truncheon may be used in lieu of conversation, words will always retain their power)"},{"pid":"7fcb498684e9923291181b64f657ea6b1fd3a0a5","tid":1351704,"uid":259329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T17:09:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"019509e9bb73161d0368d43d1fd3215d3f282cd6","tid":1351704,"uid":12278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T17:10:45.000Z","msg":"唔好再理達哥啦<br />\n佢講野關你地撚事咩<br />\n針對<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">五大訴求！</span></span>"},{"pid":"6782261d419e93a865fd9f65c74a3e3060a15d57","tid":1351704,"uid":264197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T17:11:07.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ea1ba2ec242f92bc32796f89f22224834934b881","tid":1351704,"uid":79611,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T17:11:55.000Z","msg":"香港人有個特質就係容易習慣<br />\n下次再好似今日咁就無乜人會驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab0b79daabc7d2779c6c7e1747fe645290bd79ea","tid":1351704,"uid":12278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T17:12:41.000Z","msg":"出面一大堆on9 post<br />\n警察會出黎講心聲？<br />\n清醒啲啦大家！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">五大訴求！</span></span>"},{"pid":"6da198ddcf8709d2d800706c14b8711426de84b8","tid":1351704,"uid":109701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T17:12:43.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e2ff7af7aeaa13b78ca85ebe238d825db3de2364","tid":1351704,"uid":206109,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T17:13:01.000Z","msg":"唔好光復元朗 伏黎架 一定會有借口出解放軍架 ，政府d棋行得好perfect，令到警察好似廢左咁，每一步都激到d市民好嬲，咁就可以放解放軍。<br />\n和理非有用架，我地唯一贏面係外國勢力，利用取消關係法去制衡大陸！最近發生事件外國勢力已經無再出聲啦，只有和理非佢地先有借口幫香港架，所謂西方民主國一定會出手制裁中國，元朗係重要 ，但係唔好意氣用事呀，專注番重點，繼續和理非做弱者 ，狗一到即散水，唔好拖住唔走，政府都吹唔漲，先會有轉機，咁樣落去只有死路一條，唔好以氣用事，我唔想再見到有人受傷，好驚會死人呀，以上係我建議，你地聽唔聽都好，萬事小心"},{"pid":"0517664ddbb1c9a2ef1e5f321e80ee2187fad03c","tid":1351704,"uid":109701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T17:13:58.000Z","msg":"共產黨越恐懼 我地越大勇氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"262de188f96b9ee29a7bd19681307bb73d8fe31e","tid":1351704,"uid":277916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T17:14:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"07c58781f2cc18a94f5e473e8940eed69efaa08f","tid":1351704,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T17:14:53.000Z","msg":"沒有舞蹈的革命，是不值得發動的革命。」<br />\n係咩意思？"},{"pid":"51563883c36c5b04af55273f73b3ff8c48ac7e12","tid":1351704,"uid":131259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T17:17:18.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"aa45f0c81697386f83c953e86bd7170f7e006c96","tid":1351704,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T17:17:54.000Z","msg":"沒有舞蹈的革命，是不值得發動的革命。」<br />\n係咩意思？"},{"pid":"8c31cac072a19d807450e9b506c65d04483a2062","tid":1351704,"uid":263218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T17:18:02.000Z","msg":"推動依場運動的能量<br />\n <br />\n1. 對政府長久以來的不滿<br />\n2. 仇恨憤怒<br />\n3. 對離逝的人的歉疚<br />\n4. 想香港變好的心（最重要 別忘記）"},{"pid":"88137533e7fcbdb02ac11322087f5d2ce4c2e736","tid":1351704,"uid":173002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T17:18:34.000Z","msg":"元朗單襲擊發生係西鐵，屬於鐵路恐怖襲擊。"},{"pid":"d7e598df551530d9e4e108a411eec13c084b0d93","tid":1351704,"uid":169074,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T17:20:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"66689a9731197dea29c7e618379f020175da7880","tid":1351704,"uid":276527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T17:20:56.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"c1a4bc9de301d31e9879e9b6505af9ac74521867","tid":1351704,"uid":36088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T17:21:01.000Z","msg":"up"},{"pid":"d3a14956594fe90a9e31793423afd0a94ae88636","tid":1351704,"uid":12278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T17:22:15.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"016afd88eb87301300cdcd2157788ca81531b8d2","tid":1351704,"uid":74888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T17:23:19.000Z","msg":"推呀！！"},{"pid":"d40d649aecf40d0ae4b6ac8e87026e5933259a31","tid":1351704,"uid":12278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T17:28:21.000Z","msg":"推"}]}